nodefinder
Strategies for automatic node discovery in Erlang

Imported from
http://code.google.com/p/nodefinder/


===
Configuration:
{nodefinder,
   [{addr, {224,0,0,1}},    % This is a multicast address not yours!
    {port, 1234},           % the port to multicast on
    {multicast_ttl, 10}]}   % a TTL
